## Manifest Registration

The following commands were run through `cargo run --bin qatq -- fixture add`.
The manifest paths were then normalized from `captures/...` to `../captures/...`
because `fixture add` validates paths relative to the current working directory,
while `fixture verify` and `qatq-bench` resolve relative paths from the manifest
location.

